Package: modelLong
Type: Package
Title: Model and visualize longitudinal data
Version: 1.0
Author: Alejandro Dionicio Hernandez
Maintainer: Alejandro Dionicio Hernandez <alejh@uw.edu>
Description: Package for easy fitting of linear mixed-effects models (LMM) and generalized estimating equations (GEE) for longitudinal data. Additional functions simplify creating GGPlot objects and constructing comprehensive data summaries.  
